ue\n\n## Operators\n\nAvaliable operators\n\nOperator| Description| MongoDB  \n---|---|---  \n:| Equal| {<db_field>:{$eq:<value>}}  \n!:| Not equal| {<db_field>:{$ne:<value>}}  \n  \n## About\n\n\u2699\ufe0f FaableQL is a query syntax with MongoDB support\n\nwww.npmjs.com/package/@faable/faableql\n\n### Topics\n\nmongodb mongodb-atlas faable faableql\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\nActivity\n\nCustom properties\n\n### Stars\n\n2 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n0 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n1 fork\n\nReport repository\n\n## Languages\n\n  * TypeScript 100.0%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
